default&#xa0;default&#xa0;defaultBuilding Societies in defaultNIdefaultThe main building societies with branch facilities in NI are Nationwide and the Progressive. Nationwide offer a range of curren
defaultt account services. They have 14
default main branche
defaults.
default As mentioned at the committee on 11 September, there have been closures of agency services
default provided by
default Nationwide in the past. Nationwide previously had nine agencies (private insurance brokers and estate agents) operating in NI that carried a small float to service customers with current accounts. All of these agencies closed in 2008. Consumers must now visit one of the 14 branches for face to face service.
